data.description: Welcome home or create a dream Airbnb.  This coxy retreat offers all you need off a paved road -3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms a shed and an above ground saltwater pool with deck.  This serene location sits on 1.25 acres not far from Kaw Lake.  It even comes with a 50 amp hook up for your camper! Call me today to book your private tour.
